---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Start Here — Fabric Planning"
  description="The step before your first step with Microsoft Fabric Planning — a guided starting point for finance and data teams."
>
  <!-- ── Page hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container page-hero-inner">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="section-no">§</span> Start here</span>
      <h1>The step before your <span class="italic">first step.</span></h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub">
        A guided starting point for finance and data teams sizing up Microsoft
        Fabric Planning &mdash; what to read first, what to try, and what to
        ignore for now.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Content ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="slab" style="padding-top: 88px;">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="about-prose" style="max-width: 68ch;">
        <p>
          The step before your first step is the one most people skip: deciding
          whether Fabric Planning is even worth your attention yet. Before you
          spin up a capacity or rebuild a model, it helps to understand what the
          capability is, where it sits in the Fabric stack, and which problems it
          actually solves today.<br />
          <a
            href="https://fabricplanning.substack.com/p/fabric-plan-step-zero"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            fabricplanning.substack.com/p/fabric-plan-step-zero
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="block">
        <div class="soft-panel">
          <h3>Coming soon</h3>
          <p>
            We&rsquo;re putting the finishing touches on the Start Here guide.
            Subscribe on Substack to be notified when it goes live.
          </p>
          <a
            class="btn btn-primary"
            href="https://fabricplanning.substack.com"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Subscribe on Substack <span class="arr">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
